  "security_notes": [
    "/metrics endpoint should not require authentication within trusted network but should be firewalled from public internet",
    "Consider adding basic auth or bearer token for metrics endpoint in multi-tenant deployments",
    "Prometheus data contains sensitive information about request patterns - secure appropriately",
    "Jaeger traces may contain user data - implement trace sampling and data retention policies",
    "AlertManager webhooks should use TLS and HMAC signature verification",
    "Grafana should use strong admin passwords and integrate with auth-service for SSO",
    "Business metrics should exclude PII in labels to avoid storing personal data in Prometheus"
  ],
